	<brief_description>
		Main OpenTelemetry API for traces, metrics, and logs export via OTLP.
	</brief_description>
	<description>
		OpenTelemetry provides a complete implementation of the OpenTelemetry Protocol (OTLP) for Godot Engine. It supports distributed tracing with spans, metrics collection (counters, gauges, histograms), and structured logging. Data is exported via HTTP/JSON to OTLP collectors.
		Key features include multi-sink support for redundant export, automatic batching, UUID v7 trace IDs, and comprehensive span lifecycle management.
	</description>
